## Push Summary — skrptiq-cli (main)

### What shipped
Implemented 12 read-side slash commands querying real engine data (GH#434):

| Command | What it does |
|---|---|
| `/list [type]` | List all nodes, optionally filtered (workflows, skills, prompts, etc.) |
| `/show <name>` | Display node content, type, and description |
| `/search <query>` | Search nodes by title |
| `/runs` | Execution history (placeholder — needs ListExecutions in storage) |
| `/profile [list]` | List all profiles with active indicator |
| `/dials` | Show persona dials from active voice profile metadata |
| `/mcp` | Show MCP server connections with status indicators |
| `/providers` | List AI providers with connection status |
| `/workspace` | Show workspace path, profile, and database path |
| `/tags` | List all tags with colour indicators |
| `/config` | Show key settings (provider, model, workspace, theme) |
| `/hub` | List Hub imports with versions |

### Architecture
- `internal/app/handlers.go` — all command handlers, cleanly separated from app model
- `internal/engine/engine.go` — added FindNodeByTitle, SearchNodes, HubImports, Setting
- Command routing refactored: handleSlashCommand → demo views → deferred → unknown

